# SQL Injection Demo (Secure vs Vulnerable)

This project demonstrates how **SQL Injection** works and how it can be prevented using secure coding practices.

It contains two login methods:

-  Vulnerable Login (unsafe query building)
-  Secure Login (prepared statement simulation)

The project is built using:

- HTML
- CSS
- JavaScript

---

##  Project Objective

The main objective of this project is to understand:

- What SQL Injection is
- How attackers bypass authentication
- Why dynamic query concatenation is dangerous
- How prepared statements prevent SQL Injection

---

##  Project Preview

Features available in UI:

- Username input  
- Password input  
- Vulnerable Login button  
- Secure Login button  
- Query display  
- Login result message  

